{"tid":2149283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 黑警拎左幾個伺服器，營業部同事主機及《蘋果》基金的日常運作文件","createTime":"2020-08-10T10:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T15:33:33.000Z","uid":22556,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce679bd465a98ace4b82dfe174755439687e4a8","tid":2149283,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"今日（10日）壹傳媒創辦人黎智英及多名《蘋果日報》高層被警方以涉嫌違反《國安法》拘捕，約200名警方大舉進入《蘋果》大樓進行搜證，除了翻查《蘋果》2樓編採部辦公室的員工桌上資料外，更一度封鎖3樓行政部及4樓的集團秘書部、財務部及人力資源部門搜查，同時要求進入大樓伺服器房間內取走伺服器。另外，警方亦搜查財務部員工的辦公桌及取走《蘋果》基金的日常運作文件。<br />\n<br />\n據知，警方要求查看伺服器數據及檔案等，但職員拒絕，而律師已在現場指出，伺服器內有新聞材料，搜查令不准取新聞材料，因此拒絕，雙方一度僵持不下。警員其後要求取走整部伺服器以作證物。除了伺服器房間外，亦有警員搜查集團非執董葉一堅的房間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/ZX54D7UD7PINP5Z35EGWYE52CU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FZX54D7UD7PINP5Z35EGWYE52CU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=a169599a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FZX54D7UD7PINP5Z35EGWYE52CU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e1c12c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/ZX54D7UD7PINP5Z35EGWYE52CU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"effb4c1d98103f6e2a0c0f9333088b93ecb428c0","tid":2149283,"uid":244346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a7152acda28d83fefb3e6aac50f65711baebae","tid":2149283,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike